.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-DASHBOARD-DIFF 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.9.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-dashboard\-diff \- Compare local dashboard files against live Grafana dashboards.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util dashboard diff [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Compare local dashboard files against live Grafana dashboards.
.PP
Use this when you want to see what would change before importing or publishing a dashboard bundle.
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-input\-dir
compare this export directory against Grafana.
.TP
.B \-\-input\-format
choose raw or provisioning.
.TP
.B \-\-import\-folder\-uid
override the destination folder UID for the comparison.
.TP
.B \-\-context\-lines
unified diff context.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Compare local dashboard files against live Grafana dashboards.
.EX
grafana-util dashboard diff --url http://localhost:3000 --basic-user admin --basic-password admin --input-dir ./dashboards/raw
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBgrafana-util\fR(1),
\fBgrafana-util-dashboard\fR(1)
